(% class=&amp;#34;western&amp;#34; %)
==== Energy from the Sun gets taken and challenged-forth by the selfish “rational utilitarian subject” of modern technology—status quo notions of Mastery enframe everything in standing reserve, which creates an ongoing logic of concentration camps and destruction of the earth in error replication. ====

(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in&amp;#34; %)
(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:1.0em;&amp;#34; %)**Stoekl ‘7**(%%) (% style=&amp;#34;font-size:0.8em;&amp;#34; %)(Allan Stoekl, “Bataille’s Peak Energy, Religion, and Postsustainability,” p. 128-133, 2007) [m leap]

(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in&amp;#34; %)


