(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in&amp;#34; %)


(% class=&amp;#34;western&amp;#34; %)
==== What makes the Sun shine? Blood. Blood powers the Sun. We should take a page from the Aztecs and the sacrificial Sun Festival. ====

(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in&amp;#34; %)
(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:1.0em;&amp;#34; %)**Bataille ’91**(%%) (Georges, insane librarian, The Accursed Share: An Essay on the General Economy vol. 1 consumption, translated Robert Hurley p. 48-51) [m leap]

